  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "七十二、社会主义教育运动（上）",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_3_22705-23019",
          "range": "22705-23019",
          "rangeStart": 22705,
          "rangeEnd": 23019,
          "markText": "《七律·吊罗荣桓同志》。\n记得当年草上飞，红军队里每相违。\n长征不是难堪日，战锦方为大问题。\n斥￼每闻欺大鸟，昆鸡长笑老鹰非。\n君今不幸离人世，国有疑难可问谁？",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738907247,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-02-07 13:47:27",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22705&rangeEnd=23019",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22705&rangeEnd=23019"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_3_9463-9529",
          "range": "9463-9529",
          "rangeStart": 9463,
          "rangeEnd": 9529,
          "markText": "是，九日毛泽东接到周恩来来信，希望向他汇报关于“跃进号”失事的处理情况，同时想就便在杭州与各中央局书记谈谈粮食、精简和农业生产问题。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711344062,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-25 13:21:02",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9463&rangeEnd=9529",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9463&rangeEnd=9529"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_3_3764-3801",
          "range": "3764-3801",
          "rangeStart": 3764,
          "rangeEnd": 3801,
          "markText": "这个报告第一次提出“四清”问题，即“清理账目、清理仓库、清理工分、清理财务",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711344061,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-25 13:21:01",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3764&rangeEnd=3801",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3764&rangeEnd=3801"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "chapterTitle": "八十三、临终的日子",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_14_7968-8070",
          "range": "7968-8070",
          "rangeStart": 7968,
          "rangeEnd": 8070,
          "markText": "“民主革命后，工人、贫下中农没有停止，他们要革命。而一部分党员却不想前进了，有些人后退了，反对革命了。为什么呢？作了大官了，要保护大官们的利益。他们有了好房子，有汽车，薪水高，还有服务员，比资本家还厉害。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711768738,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-30 11:18:58",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=7968&rangeEnd=8070",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=7968&rangeEnd=8070"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "chapterTitle": "八十、十大前后",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_11_29778-29971",
          "range": "29778-29971",
          "rangeStart": 29778,
          "rangeEnd": 29971,
          "markText": "又着重向大家谈了邓小平，说：“我们现在请了一位总参谋长。他呢，有些人怕他，他是办事比较果断。他一生大概是三七开。你们的老上司，我请回来了，政治局请回来了，不是我一个人请回来的。你呢（指邓小平——引者注），人家有点怕你，我送你两句话：柔中寓刚，绵里藏针。外面和气一点，内部是钢铁公司。过去的缺点，慢慢地改一改吧。不做工作，就不会犯错误。一做工作，总要犯错误的。不做工作本身也是一个错误。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711723842,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-29 22:50:42",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=29778&rangeEnd=29971",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=29778&rangeEnd=29971"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_11_31282-31295",
          "range": "31282-31295",
          "rangeStart": 31282,
          "rangeEnd": 31295,
          "markText": "常恨随陆无武，绛灌无文’。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711723841,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-29 22:50:41",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=31282&rangeEnd=31295",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=31282&rangeEnd=31295"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "七十八、林彪事件",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_9_39996-40165",
          "range": "39996-40165",
          "rangeStart": 39996,
          "rangeEnd": 40165,
          "markText": "毛泽东到南昌时，听取江西省负责人的汇报，引起他注意的主要有三点：一、这年七月周宇驰曾两次秘密来江西活动；二、庐山会议期间叶群确有“不设国家主席，林彪往哪里摆”的说法；三、林彪之女林立衡关于“同林彪家人来往，搞不好要杀头”的警告。据陪同毛泽东南巡的张耀祠回忆，听了这些反映后，毛泽东“略有所思，把眼睛眯成了一条线，远眺窗外，没有讲一句话”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711627984,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 20:13:04",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=39996&rangeEnd=40165",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=39996&rangeEnd=40165"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_9_28158-28466",
          "range": "28158-28466",
          "rangeStart": 28158,
          "rangeEnd": 28466,
          "markText": "十二月十八日，毛泽东在他的书房里饶有兴致地接待了他的美国老朋友埃德加·斯诺，同他进行了话题广泛的交谈。其中多次谈到关于“个人崇拜”和“文化大革命”的问题。以下是两个人的一段对话：“毛：现在就不同了，崇拜得过分了，搞许多形式主义。比如什么‘四个伟大’，‘Great Teacher, Great Leader, Great Supreme Commander, Great Helmsman'（伟大导师，伟大领袖，伟大统帅，伟大舵手），讨嫌！总有一天要统统去掉，只剩下一个‘Teacher'，就是教员。因为我历来是当教员的，现在还是当教员。其他的一概辞去",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711618300,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 17:31:40",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=28158&rangeEnd=28466",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=28158&rangeEnd=28466"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "七十九、一九七二年的内政和外交",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_10_16676-16687",
          "range": "16676-16687",
          "rangeStart": 16676,
          "rangeEnd": 16687,
          "markText": "高筑墙，广积粮，缓称王",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711627983,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 20:13:03",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=16676&rangeEnd=16687",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=16676&rangeEnd=16687"
        }
