    {
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "chapterTitle": "八十二、支持全面整顿到“反击右倾翻案风”",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_13_25984-26023",
          "range": "25984-26023",
          "rangeStart": 25984,
          "rangeEnd": 26023,
          "markText": "毛泽东自言自语道：“我这个人感情越来越脆弱了。我一听到天灾人祸，就忍不住伤心。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711618301,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 17:31:41",
          "chapterUid": 13,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=25984&rangeEnd=26023",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=25984&rangeEnd=26023"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_13_13457-13465",
          "range": "13457-13465",
          "rangeStart": 13457,
          "rangeEnd": 13465,
          "markText": "不尽长江滚滚流。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711618300,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 17:31:40",
          "chapterUid": 13,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=13457&rangeEnd=13465",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=13457&rangeEnd=13465"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "七十六、在“全面夺权”的日子里",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_7_12691-12770",
          "range": "12691-12770",
          "rangeStart": 12691,
          "rangeEnd": 12770,
          "markText": "二月十九日，毛泽东对北京卫戍区在北大、清华等五所高等院校和两所中学实行短期军训试点工作的两个总结报告批示：“大学、中学和小学高年级每年训练一次，每次二十天。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711618299,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 17:31:39",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640918&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12691&rangeEnd=12770",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/821326e07168bb56821d48f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12691&rangeEnd=12770"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23640918_7_23389-23430",
          "range": "23389-23430",
          "rangeStart": 23389,
          "rangeEnd": 23430,
          "markText": "知识分子从来是转变、察觉问题快，但受到本能的限制，缺乏彻底革命性，往往带有投机性。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1711618298,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-28 17:31:38",
          "chapterUid": 7,
